title: Migration Routes from Europe to Africa
description: A simplified map showing various migration routes from Europe to Africa. The routes are represented by colored arrows: yellow, green, red, and blue, indicating different paths taken. The map outlines the geographical locations of Europe and Africa, highlighting the connections between the two continents.

title: Animal Jawbone
description: A detailed illustration of an animal jawbone, showcasing its structure and teeth. The jawbone is depicted in a side view, highlighting the curvature and the prominent canine tooth.

title: Close-up of a Bird
description: A close-up image of a bird, showcasing its detailed features. The bird has a distinctive beak that is slightly curved, with a mix of yellow and grayish feathers on its head and neck. The background is blurred, emphasizing the bird's face.
